{% doc %}
  @prompt
    Create a responsive testimonials slider that displays 3 customer reviews at once. Include circular customer profile images, 5-star rating displays, customer testimonial text, and customer name headings. Add navigation controls (previous/next buttons) and enable auto-sliding functionality with customizable settings (auto-slide speed, pause on hover, enable/disable auto-slide). Make the slider fully responsive for mobile, tablet, and desktop devices with admin settings panel.

{% enddoc %}
{% assign ai_gen_id = block.id | replace: '_', '' | downcase %}

{% style %}
